name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Raynard TAYLOR, Petitioner

parties: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Raynard TAYLOR, Petitioner.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 10th day of February, 2012, the Petition for Leave to File Petition for Allowance of Appeal Nunc Pro Tunc is GRANTED. Counsel is directed to file a Petition for Allowance of Appeal within 30 days of this order.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
